## 13. Главный мастер-промт для генерации UI-kit

Использовать в ChatGPT Images / Firefly / Midjourney / Figma AI как основу.

```text
Create a complete luxury UI button design system for a culinary recipe calculator app, based on the provided reference button style. Premium pastry interface, pearl luxury, warm gold trim, soft neumorphism, tactile decorative realism. Create a polished UI kit sheet showing a full family of buttons: long primary capsule buttons, medium oval buttons, small utility buttons, circular icon medallion buttons, toggle buttons, print/export buttons, navigation buttons.

Each button should feature a luminous mother-of-pearl inner surface with shell-like iridescent textures in creamy champagne, blush beige, soft rose pearl, pale lilac pearl, warm ivory and golden highlights. Use layered polished gold borders, elegant embossed golden typography, soft studio lighting, subtle glassy gloss, refined shadows, and rich tactile depth.

Include button types for: Add New Recipe, Save Recipe, Edit, Delete, Add Ingredient, Collapse All, Expand All, Save PDF, Print Tech Card, Print Shopping List, Import, Export, Choose Photo, Crop Photo, Background Settings, Preview, Confirm, Cancel, Back, Next, Open, Close.

Include circular icon buttons for plus, minus, pencil, trash, printer, pdf, arrows, expand, collapse, upload, download, save.

Show button states: normal, hover, pressed, active, disabled.

The whole composition should look like a cohesive premium design system board for a high-end pastry-themed application, elegant, warm, detailed, readable, and luxurious. Preserve tactile 3D depth, pearl texture, warm gold framing, and premium readable typography.

Avoid flat design, cheap plastic, neon gold, chrome metal, sci-fi interface, cyberpunk, childish cartoon buttons, low detail, blurry text, harsh shadows, cold silver palette, generic mobile UI, poor readability, clutter, oversaturated colors, low quality textures, rough edges, plain gradients.
```

